| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2022-1761 — Recovery Inhibition (alphv)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: a7baf676-f0d2-5ab8-be11-4f6a2ae6337c"
